<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-170] Schema validation aginst Log4J-V2.0.xsd fails</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-170</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Log4J-V2.0.xsd is outdated. The type of element &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt; lacks attributes &quot;verbose&quot;, &quot;monitorInterval&quot;, &quot;dest&quot; and even &quot;schema&quot; for enabling schema validation :o&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;configuration strict=&quot;true&quot; schema=&quot;Log4J-V2.0.xsd&quot; status=&quot;OFF&quot;  monitorInterval=&quot;300&quot;&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Enables validation and makes it fail right after.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
